FeatureItem.Title: Member Bird List
FeatureItem.Description: Birds our members raise: East African Cranes, Pheasants (30 types), Peacocks (3 types), Ducks (24 types), Partridge (5 types), Quail (10 types), Geese (5 types), Pigeons, Doves (3 types), Emu, Guinea Fowl, Turkeys, Swans, Red Jungle Fowl, and Heirloom Chickens.
